game.name: Breakfast Time
game.description:
Your boss has left the town for some important work and you are her first choice to take care of her responsibilities. Join Breakfast Time and be prepared to take her place at the nursery! Most of working women drop their kids off with you at this place. This clears that you have to deal with lots children around you with hungry tummies. They come one by one and ask you their favourite food. Take a charge of a chef and get ready to serve their desired healthy food in this girls game!

You have available a wide range of healthy meals for them in your kitchen. Your job in this cool cooking game is to serve their favorite food items before the time expires. Try to give them exactly what they ask for to secure some points! Be careful and make sure that you prepare correct breakfast for these cute babies! Your every successful effort rewards you with some money. Every wrong decision like making them wait too long or giving them the wrong food will lose your money.

The upper side of the screen will show you customers while the bottom area of the screen will show you the items available at your nursery. Track what meals they need by looking your eyes at the top right corner of the screen in this amazing food game! Our website is full of girls cooking games that are playable on multiple devices. Choose any of the best girls games and have a blast online with your friends!!
